<p>
Welcome to the second issue of the new look Muddled Times. Included in this issue is an interview with Crowley and the first two articles taken from the list in <span class="missing">"What articles would you like to see in Muddled Times?"</span>
<p>
In addition to the new format launched in the previous issue further changes to Muddled Times that can be seen in this issue are:
<ul>
<li>A new and improved search facility
<li>Improved navigation of each issue
<li>If you click on an author name you will see a list of all articles by that author
<li>A different front 'cover' for each issue
</ul><p>
If you are feeling artistic please feel free to design a future 'cover' for Muddled Times. This design must be in-keeping with the style and feel of Muddled Times, and also must be orginal. The current design is "Dragon in the Mist" by <a href="http://www.peterpracownik.com/frames.htm">Peter Pracownik</a> for which we have permission to use.
<p>
You can contribute to Muddled Times, by either providing articles, or making comments using the "author feedback" system (click the link below the relevant article), or even just sending in an image for <a href="personae.fod">Persona Pictures</a>.
<P>
Please send in any articles you have to me at <span class="missing">karya@muddled-times.com</span>.
<p>
Thank you!
<p>
<b><i>Karya</i></b>
